OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will gradually
OL,6,Fmove eastwards across the UK today,
OL,7,Falthough not reaching the southeast
OL,8,Funtil evening. Largely dry, bright and
OL,9,Fwarm ahead of the rain, with blustery
OL,10,Fand occasionally heavy showers
OL,11,Ffollowing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe rain continues to clear
OL,14,Feastwards and weaken as it does so.
OL,15,FOtherwise, showers continuing across
OL,16,Fnorthern areas, especially western
OL,17,FScotland and Northern Ireland, but
OL,18,Fbecoming largely dry elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
