OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAny lingering rain across
OL,6,Fthe far southeast will clear during
OL,7,Fthe morning, leaving many southern
OL,8,Fareas largely dry with sunny spells.
OL,9,FScattered showers elsewhere, although
OL,10,Ftending to ease later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
